
                       RELNOTES for Falcon 0.8.6

   This version of Falcon comes with a brand new functional support
and with new Message Oriented programming constructs.

   Although stable, this features may be reshaped and refitted as 
they are relatively new.

   This version comes with a brand new "Showdown" guide introducing
the most intriguing features of the language at grammar level. The
guide can be downloaded at Falcon Site

    http://www.falconpl.org

under the "documentation" section.

